lyrics:

I will not bow

I will not fall
I will not fade
I will take your breath away

Fall

Take the fall and run to Heaven

All is lost again
But I'm not giving in

I will not bow
I will not break
I will shut the world away
I will not fall
I will not fade
I will take your breath away

And I'll survive, paranoid
I have lost the will to change
And I'm not proud, cold-blooded fate
I will shut the world away

(Open your eyes)

I will not bow
